text: That is only the case of the nostalgics of former communist regime, today voters of AUR/SOS/to some extent PSD. And even among them there an obvious frustration every time Nawrocki says something negative about Russia.

Poland’s Catholic President Karol Nawrocki: "I will not sign any law that undermines the unique and constitutionally protected status of marriage.”

🇵🇱 Polish President Nawrocki supported the decision not to extradite the Ukrainian to Germany in the "Nord Stream" case I agree that he may not receive a fair trial from the German side, since "Nord Stream 2" was a project aimed at generating profit for the German state. This is about an agreement between a state that subsidized the aggressor by buying gas and the aggressor state. A Ukrainian citizen cannot be punished for such activity while his country is being devastated by Putin 🥂 Volodymyr Zhuravlyov, whom the Germans suspect of involvement in the sabotage of the pipelines, stated that he did not sabotage anything No, I did not commit any crime on German territory and did not sabotage the "Nord Stream" 🇮🇹 Recently, the German authorities received a similar refusal from the Italian court, which also refused to extradite the suspect in the sabotage of the "Nord Stream" pipeline. A jak tam sprawa wyłudzenia mieszkania pana Jerzego? Nawet jeżeli dla niektórych Nawrocki ma immunitet, to już Nawrocka go nie ma. A współudział też jest przestępstwem. Taki żarcik, w Polsce nikt nie ma na to jaj.

🇵🇱🇺🇦 Polish President Nawrocki supported the decision not to extradite a Ukrainian suspected of the Nord Stream explosions to Germany: “I agree that he may not receive a fair trial from the German side, since Nord Stream 2 was a project aimed at making a profit for the German state. This is an agreement between a state that subsidized the aggressor by buying gas and the aggressor state. A citizen of Ukraine cannot be punished for such activities at a time when his country is being devastated by Putin.” Ukrainian Volodymyr Zhuravlev, who is suspected in Germany of the gas pipeline explosions, denied all charges: “No, I did not commit any crime on the territory of Germany and did not undermine Nord Stream.” Earlier, a court in Italy made a similar decision — they also refused to extradite another suspect to Germany.

🇺🇦🇩🇪🇵🇱🇷🇺 Le président polonais Karol Nawrocki a soutenu la décision de ne pas extrader vers l'Allemagne un Ukrainien soupçonné d'être à l'origine des explosions de Nord Stream 2 : « Je conviens qu'il pourrait ne pas bénéficier d'un procès équitable de la part de l'Allemagne, car Nord Stream 2 était un projet visant à générer des profits pour l'État allemand. Il s'agit d'un accord entre un État qui a subventionné l'agresseur en achetant du gaz et l'État agresseur. Un citoyen ukrainien ne peut être puni pour de telles activités à un moment où son pays est dévasté par Poutine. »

🇵🇱🇺🇦 Polish President Nawrocki supported the decision not to extradite a Ukrainian suspected of the Nord Stream explosions to Germany: “I agree that he may not receive a fair trial from the German side, since Nord Stream 2 was a project aimed at making a profit for the German state. This is an agreement between a state that subsidized the aggressor by buying gas and the aggressor state. A citizen of Ukraine cannot be punished for such activities at a time when his country is being devastated by Putin.” Ukrainian Volodymyr Zhuravlev, who is suspected in Germany of the gas pipeline explosions, denied all charges: “No, I did not commit any crime on the territory of Germany and did not undermine Nord Stream.” Earlier, a court in Italy made a similar decision — they also refused to extradite another suspect to Germany.

A citizen of Ukraine cannot be punished for such activities at a time when his country is being devastated by Putin.” Ukrainian Volodymyr Zhuravlev, who is suspected in Germany of the gas pipeline explosions, denied all charges: “No, I did not commit any crime on the territory of Germany and did not undermine Nord Stream.” Earlier, a court in Italy made a similar decision — they also refused to extradite another suspect to Germany.
#prezydentRP #Nawrocki #włączprawdę #TVRepublika
